"title": "4684: sheep",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4684",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sheep were a major feature of ancient Israel's rural economy. Although they were of importance as a source of food and wool, they also symbolise helplessness and the need for guidance.</p>\n<h2>The economic importance of sheep</h2>\n<h3>As a measure of wealth and God's blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:2\">1SA 25:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:13\">PSA 144:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:16\">GEN 12:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:43\">GEN 30:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:3\">EXO 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:1\">EXO 22:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:1-Deut22:2\">DEU 22:1–22:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:21\">JOS 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:2-2Sam12:3\">2SA 12:2–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:3\">JOB 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:12\">JOB 42:12</a></p>\n<h3>As a source of food</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:18\">1SA 25:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:23\">LEV 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:17-Num18:18\">NUM 18:17–18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:32\">1SA 14:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:40\">1CH 12:40</a></p>\n<h3>As a source of wool</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:4\">2KI 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:19\">GEN 31:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:12-Gen38:13\">GEN 38:12–38:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:4\">DEU 18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:7\">1SA 25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:23-2Sam13:24\">2SA 13:23–13:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:18\">EZK 27:18</a></p>\n<h3>Sheep were used in striking a bargain</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:27\">GEN 21:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:14\">GEN 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:25-Gen30:43\">GEN 30:25–30:43</a></p>\n<h3>The care of sheep was a recognised occupation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:11\">1SA 16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:2-Gen29:3\">GEN 29:2–29:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:13\">GEN 37:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:34-1Sam17:35\">1SA 17:34–17:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:7\">SNG 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:12\">HOS 12:12</a></p>\n<h2>Sheep were used in sacrifice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:24\">EXO 20:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:10\">LEV 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:19\">LEV 22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:23\">LEV 22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:40\">NUM 22:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:3\">DEU 18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:9\">1KI 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:5\">1KI 8:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:14\">JHN 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>The symbolic importance of sheep</h2>\n<h3>Israel without a leader</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:17\">1KI 22:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:16-Num27:17\">NUM 27:16–27:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:17\">2SA 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:7\">ZEC 13:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31\">MAT 26:31</a></p>\n<h3>Helplessness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7\">ISA 53:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:36\">MAT 9:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:11\">PSA 44:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:14\">PSA 49:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:3\">JER 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:16\">MAT 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:36\">ROM 8:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:22\">PSA 44:22</a></p>\n<h3>Judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:32-Matt25:33\">MAT 25:32–25:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:17\">EZK 34:17</a></p>\n<h3>Sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:6\">ISA 53:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:25\">1PE 2:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:176\">PSA 119:176</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:12\">MAT 18:12</a></p>\n<h3>The people that belong to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:3\">PSA 100:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:1\">PSA 74:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:52\">PSA 78:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:13\">PSA 79:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:1\">JER 23:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:6\">JER 50:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:11-Ezek34:15\">EZK 34:11–34:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:12\">MIC 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's care for his own</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:32\">LUK 12:32</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:16\">JHN 10:1–10:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:26-John10:30\">JHN 10:26–10:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:16-John21:17\">JHN 21:16–21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20\">HEB 13:20</a></p>\n<h3>A picture of God's future blessings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:17\">ISA 5:17</a></strong></p>",
